{"chunks": [{"text": "[1-dars (namuna dars)]\n# 1-dars: Namuna kirish darsi (test uchun)\n\n## Mavzu: Python o'zgaruvchilari\n\nPython'da o'zgaruvchi yaratish juda oson. Siz shunchaki nom va qiymat yozasiz:\n\n```python\nism = \"Ali\"\nyosh = 25\nboyi = 1.75\n```\n\nPython o'zgaruvchi turini avtomatik aniqlaydi. Bu — **dynamic typing** deb ataladi.\n\n## O'zgaruvchi nomlash qoidalari\n\n1. Faqat harf, raqam va `_` belgisidan foydalanish mumkin\n2. Raqam bilan boshlanmasligi kerak\n3. Probel ishlatib bo'lmaydi\n4. O'zbek harflari texnik jihatdan ishlaydi, lekin tavsiya etilmaydi\n\n**To'g'ri misollar:** `talaba_ismi`, `yosh`, `_yashirin`, `son1`\n**Noto'g'ri misollar:** `1-talaba`, `talaba ismi`, `talaba!`\n\n## Uy vazifasi\n\n3 ta o'zgaruvchi yarating: ismingiz, yoshingiz va boyingiz. Keyin ularni `print()` orqali ekranga chiqaring.", "source": "01-namuna-dars.md", "chunk_id": 0, "module": "", "lesson": "1"}], "embeddings": [[-0.012596501968801022, -0.007533007767051458, 0.01689738593995571, -0.05701635405421257, -0.005772770848125219, 0.005025705322623253, -0.008284248411655426, 0.004681386519223452, -0.0005060168914496899, 0.010743259452283382, -0.021982675418257713, -0.01910756342113018, -0.011898811906576157, 0.004905620124191046, 0.1351069211959839, 0.0037517782766371965, -0.0031754563096910715, 0.0011571303475648165, -0.004234822932630777, -0.021785972639918327, 0.00580322090536356, 0.006483541335910559, 0.0069670784287154675, -0.003224771237000823, -0.0004833241691812873, 0.0014170053182169795, 0.009115159511566162, 0.01717536337673664, 0.016881980001926422, -0.012104629538953304, -0.005498602986335754, 0.012116768397390842, 0.005119023844599724, 0.016303667798638344, -0.0190450306981802, 0.009691360406577587, 0.030324922874569893, 0.008472020737826824, -0.010715045034885406, 0.023243939504027367, -0.016795331612229347, -0.0029764515347778797, -0.005114573985338211, -0.01142546720802784, 0.012372882105410099, 0.000691138906404376, 0.0013940364588052034, -0.03